      "span_text": "siNF-κB p65 (sense, 5′-CCAUCAACUAUGAUGAGUUdTdT-3′ and antisense, 3′-dGdTGGUAGUU-GAUACUACUCAA-5′) was designed to target the NF-κB p65 and was produced by GenePharma [CITATION_1] ."
